New reposity->Addname->Add description->Make it public -> Remote repository created

git init :To create a local repository

To create local branches :

git branch Dev
git branch QA
git branch Feature
git branch Delivery
master branch exists by default 

To test :
  git branch
  Delivery
* Dev(Current branch)
  QA
  feature
  master
  
  
To create remote branches :
git push origin Dev
git push origin QA
git push origin Feature
git push origin Delivery








